{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 180°C. Line a baking tray with baking paper and set aside. Grease Varoma dish and Varoma tray.","Slice aubergines in half and score the inside using a sharp knife. Make diagonal cuts about 1 cm apart, then repeat in opposite direction to achieve a diamond pattern. Arrange 2 halves of aubergine with cut side down in prepared Varoma dish and 2 others on prepared Varoma tray. Insert Varoma tray in Varoma dish, close Varoma lid and set aside.","Place miso, mirin, sugar, sake and water in mixing bowl. Place Varoma into position and cook <nobr>15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1.5<\/nobr>. Remove Varoma.","Transfer cooked aubergines to prepared baking tray flesh side up. Brush miso mixture over each aubergine until surface is coated and bake for 35 minutes (180°C). Serve hot garnished with toasted sesame seeds."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["oil, for greasing","2 aubergines (approx. 250 g each)","4 Tbsp miso (e.g. 2 Tbsp white miso paste, 2 Tbsp red miso paste)","20 g mirin","15 g sugar","20 g sake","160 g water","1 tsp toasted sesame seeds, to garnish"]}],"id":"r211757","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-HdjPrPkme0Q\/XZVPdS-mQBI\/AAAAAAAAc48\/USQ7huFCAXIMt6VueJ6hTnu6iLrwrCO4ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_6mKEpobN3phvynAc.png","title":"Miso Glazed Aubergine (Nasu dengaku)","publishedAt":"2017-10-16T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3 g","fat":"12 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"9 g","calories":"735 kJ \/ 176 kcal"},"usefulItems":"pastry brush, baking tray and paper, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","4 portions"]}